{"uuid":"recommended71163","createDate":1643418360000,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"71163\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:06:22\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2022-01-29\",\"gameName\":\"Sonic The Hedgehog 2\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/71163\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/71163/\",\"playTime\":\"2.0\",\"updateTime\":\"2022-01-29\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"2.0\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/71163\"}","type":"steamReview","title":"评测 > Sonic The Hedgehog 2","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  ~&lt;刺猬索尼克2&gt; 世嘉MD官方ROM~\n </div>剧情很简单，小红蛋博士（Eggman博士 or Robotnik博士，管它呢~小红就是了！）回来了！\n <br>\n 他把无助的动物变成了机器人，并迫使它们制造他的终极武器——死亡蛋（一台飞船！？）！\n <br>\n 这次，索尼克有一个朋友可以帮助他：尾巴（小黄，会开飞机尾巴转起来还会飞！）\n <br>\n 然后开始救下各种小动物，然后阻止小红蛋博士的邪恶计划！\n <br>\n <br>\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  别看别人玩这游戏的时候冲的很爽快！实际玩起来极度劝退！\n  <br>\n  前期还好，最后一关那平台跳跃简直了！\n  <br>\n  小蓝刺猬脚底抹油就算了！跳起来还会变成球···\n  <br>\n  变成球就算了！这平台还会消失的！\n  <br>\n  QAQ~我这重试了不知道多少次···\n </div>\n <br>\n 游戏一共应该有17个关卡(貌似，太多了)，中间还有个伪3D版本的索尼克小游戏~\n <br>\n 基本每个关卡的目的都是解放各种小动物，最后2个关卡在空中前往死亡蛋~\n <br>\n 最后反正冲到小红蛋博士的死亡蛋飞船上冲冲冲···\n <br>\n 消灭机器索尼克最后消灭小红蛋机器人！\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736382861\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736382861</a>\n <br>\n 然后boom~索尼克从太空掉落下来，被开飞机的小黄接住~一堆小动物过来欢送他们··\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736383574\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736383574</a>\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736383973\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_2\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2736383973</a>\n <br>\n ~THE END~\n <br><span class=\"bb_spoiler\"><span> ~还好有M